      <p><a href="ch73s12.html#MonstersAnimals38">Cheetahs</a> are swift feline predators of the plains. A <a href="ch73s12.html#MonstersAnimals38">cheetah</a> is 3 to 5 feet long and weighs 110 to 130 pounds.</p>
